# 📊 Tableau Retail Sales Dashboard

This Tableau project visualizes and analyzes retail transaction data, helping uncover insights about sales performance, profit centers, and customer behavior.

---

## 📌 Objective

To build a dynamic Tableau dashboard that empowers retail business stakeholders to:
- Track regional and category-wise performance
- Identify high-value transactions and profit trends
- Evaluate customer and shipping efficiency
- Make data-driven decisions via interactive visuals

---

## 📁 Files Included

- `PROJECT.twb` – Tableau Workbook (developed in Tableau Desktop)
- `sample_data.csv` – (Optional) Sample dataset (if sharable)
- `screenshots/` – Dashboard visuals (preview)

---

