## 🔧 Tools & Technologies

- **Tableau Desktop**
- **Data Source**: Global Superstore / Custom Retail Dataset
- **Techniques Used**:
  - Calculated fields (e.g., High-Value Transactions)
  - Parameters and Filters
  - Trend Lines and Reference Bands
  - Custom Tooltips
  - Data Blending / Joins

---

## 🔍 Key Insights

- Top 20% of customers contribute over 60% of total revenue.
- Technology and Office Supplies drive high profit margins.
- Discounts don’t always lead to higher sales.
- Standard Class shipments account for maximum orders, but at lower profitability.

---

## 💻 How to Use

1. Download [Tableau Desktop](https://www.tableau.com/products/desktop) (free trial available)
2. Clone this repo or download the `.twb` file
3. Open `PROJECT.twb` in Tableau
4. If dataset is external, you may need to:
   - Relink the data source (`sample_data.csv`)
   - Refresh extracts (if used)

